Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:41.06,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}崩れゆく　こんな世界で　たったひとつ信じるのは　この心の痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:47.33,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}Black cross sorting With tears in force.
