Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:18.02,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我无须你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:22.74,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}凛冽的寒风把我的心冻伤
