Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻从机体上下来投降
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则  我不保证这女人的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快  西方总军司令部也将被我们镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜托你下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会对你们两个不利的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽姿…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西北方有不明机体接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提奥多尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  提奥多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.59,0:00:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你  没有你这家伙在的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  快点走  提奥多尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要抓住未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账  混账  混账！
